stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> queued
  queued --> running: worker picks up
  running --> running: progress updates (0..1)
  running --> succeeded: asset_ref set
  running --> failed: error{retryable?}
  failed --> queued: retry (back-off) if retryable
  running --> cancelled: cancel
  succeeded --> [*]
  cancelled --> [*]
